author: andreasmyth
msg: Removed catching of IOExceptions from RM code (remnants from Celtix Objectweb architecture).

Propagate exceptions thrown during sending of RM protocol messages where possible, i.e. in the context of processing an application (or another RM protocol) message, log as SEVERE otherwise (i.e. in tasks run by the endpoint's executor).
